{
  "chapter": 111,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述徐子陵与四大寇（毛燥、房见鼎、向霸天、曹应龙）的激烈战斗。徐子陵以螺旋真劲击败毛燥，但身负重伤。寇仲与李天凡、沈落雁展开生死搏斗，展现井中月的惊人威力。商秀洵孤身对抗贼寇，徐子陵赶来支援。最终曹应龙发现援军逼近，被迫下令撤退。本章突显了徐子陵和寇仲的武艺精进，以及四大寇的阴险狡诈。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_tian_fan",
      "speaker_name": "李天凡",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "speaker_name": "曹应龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蠢材，还不动手。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_li_tian_fan",
      "text": "走得这么容易吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_tian_fan",
      "speaker_name": "李天凡",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你的拍档在那里？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_li_tian_fan",
      "text": "收拾你这小子，只我一人就足够有馀，人家是文武兼资，你却是躲逃并备，还加上一项轻易舍弃手下的本领，真不愧李密的儿子。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_tian_fan",
      "speaker_name": "李天凡",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你想激起我的怒火吗？没有那么容易，何来这么多废话，手底下见真章吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_tian_fan",
      "speaker_name": "李天凡",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "右名射目，左名月照，能断金削玉，寇兄小心了！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天玩够了，请代小弟向密公问好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "speaker_name": "曹应龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是怎么弄的，怎会给人来到这里才知道。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "speaker_name": "曹应龙",
      "listener": "char_fang_jian_ding",
      "text": "小不忍则乱大谋，我们立即撤退。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 111,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 315
    }
  ],
